title: Lake Houston/ Kingwood New Community Premium Amenities
posting_body: ['For leasing information call or text', 'show contact info', 'today!!!', 'Ask for ID# 1449A', 'Welcome to Kingwood area’s new pet-friendly apartments near Houston.', 'Our community offers spacious one, two, and three-bedroom floor plans featuring private gated patios or balconies, oversized tubs and standing tile showers, walk-in closets, designer kitchens, and optional attached garages.', 'Live each day better than the last with a 24-hour fitness center, miles of trails, on-site pet park, and resort-style pool overlooking a 10-acre nature reserve.', 'Discover brand new designer spaces and the best in amenities at a community perfect for nature lovers and urban adventurers alike.', '24-HOUR FITNESS CENTER', 'LAKEFRONT RESORT-STYLE POOL', 'CELL PHONE CONTROLLED ACCESS GATES', 'EXECUTIVE BUSINESS CENTER', 'OUTDOOR DINING WITH GRILLING & FIRE PITS', 'HIGH-SPEED INTERNET', 'FULLY FENCED PET PARK', '10-ACRE NATURE RESERVE', 'RECREATION ROOM WITH VINTAGE ARCADE; POOL TABLE', 'RESIDENT LOUNGE & BUSINESS CENTER WITH STARBUCKS COFFEE BAR', 'CLOSE TO VALLEY RANCH TOWN CENTER']
